text.text: Carpark is huge, also next to mrt station.  Nice arena.  Small and warm.  Great Courtside view.  Choosing the right seats is important.  Not much food and drinks options. The only F&B takeaway is the size of 2 apartment toliet.

very epic arena. a lot of fights happening, some wielded. action packed fighting in hall 6 and a tense environment in hall 5 as the fighters get ready to enter the arena. a lot of blood sweat and tears are put into the fighters hard work. she hauls her equipment into hall 5 and sits down. beads of sweat trickle down her forehead as she prepares for battle. countless hours of training and dedication.
ding dong the alarm clock went off
overall nice atmosphere it gets you hyped up and the aircon is just right
